from bokeh.plotting import figure
from bokeh.resources import INLINE
from bokeh.io import output_notebook, show
import bokeh.io

x_values = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
y_values = [6, 7, 2, 3, 6]

p = figure()
p.circle(x=x_values, y=y_values)

bokeh.io.output_notebook(INLINE)
show(p)
